metadata.name: A Quiet Place in the Jungle
metadata.description:
I am a prolific artist using AI and digital art methods in conjunction to create new art - underlining "new art". I believe that this technology gives all artists the speed and confidence to push their limits, and I for one intend to!

This is a Hieronymous Bosch-inspired art I made, named "A Quiet Place in the Jungle". It represents the distractions and static we have in our lives, in the form of jungle animals and stuff... and the quest - the longing - to find a quiet, secluded place in all the mess.

The image is quite large and detailed: 10800x7333 px. Enjoy!
